>很多新装修的朋友都在疑惑要不要做吊顶，其实大家可以根据自身的具体情况来决定，综合考虑房屋层高、装修风格、个人喜好、经济成本等方面来选择采用哪种顶面装饰方式。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p>', '家装指南', '1');
INSERT INTO `tbl_news` VALUES ('30', '20180111\\c9ce8f6af814dffe79ac44e655b2f34a21733.png', '精装修房子后总结出来的9条经验！', '管理员', '2018-01-11 13:36:34', '63', '装修是一件耗时耗精力的事情。但是自己居住的场所，再麻烦也会觉得开心。可怕的是，自己精心装修完的房子，入住之后才发现后悔的事情太多，会让人倍感失落。下面小编君就给大家分享9条经验，一起看看吧。', '<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">装修是一件耗时耗精力的事情。但是自己居住的场所，再麻烦也会觉得开心。可怕的是，自己精心装修完的房子，入住之后才发现后悔的事情太多，会让人倍感失落。下面小编君就给大家分享9条经验，一起看看吧。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">冰箱放餐厅、放客厅都不如放在厨房好</span>，你想做饭，还得一趟趟的去客厅拿菜，太麻烦，动线太远了不利于生活。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKVPibFibibZGiaMtO9PBG15YhnkLYxgwibjZTc8tbDbdribHKib8UxJXfjCxibA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"500\" _width=\"auto\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKVPibFibibZGiaMtO9PBG15YhnkLYxgwibjZTc8tbDbdribHKib8UxJXfjCxibA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、做鞋柜的时候不要只贪图好看，因为住久了，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">鞋子会积累得越来越多，小鞋柜根本容不下那么多鞋子</span>，到时候更难处理，鞋子放得到处都乱糟糟，所以还在大鞋柜实用。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKTboD0jIYhIw9PrhTZIEU4gEmibZWKyuXibsuGOcmH3ACvUO5iahUZq0Vg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"500\" _width=\"auto\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKTboD0jIYhIw9PrhTZIEU4gEmibZWKyuXibsuGOcmH3ACvUO5iahUZq0Vg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3、交房后，楼上如果在装修，留个心眼看看家里的下水管，如果有这种渗水漏水的现象，二话不用说找物业和开发商去。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjK2NVdoLyMWTM4weFicBDRTzjTHDoIfsn225Zexrnic2dgh8w6yjLN3xRg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"500\" _width=\"auto\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjK2NVdoLyMWTM4weFicBDRTzjTHDoIfsn225Zexrnic2dgh8w6yjLN3xRg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">自己家里要有水管总阀，</span>万一哪天出现水管爆裂的突发状况，自己还可以控制，不然依照物业的办事效率，家都能被淹好几次了。为了全局着想，一定要装水管总阀。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">5、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">家里灯装太多，家里的射灯、过道灯,说真的装上去白白浪费了钱</span>，一年下来也就过年会开，平常都是摆设，能省的就省了吧，不实用。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">6、吧台、酒柜本来即是软肋，别以为装个吧台酒柜即是都市生活了，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">如果往常没空打理，也没有浪漫情调就别思考了，这些不只占方位，打理起来也十分费事</span>，简单积灰。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">7、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">窗帘最好在网上买，价格比较便宜</span>。如果不清楚尺寸的，就自己实测整面墙的宽度，再乘2、3、4倍，如果得出的数字比较大的话，那么出来的效果就会很好的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">8、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">电视墙必定不要为了赶潮流，做得太花哨</span>，整齐大方为妙，这么的规划就算再过个20年，也不怕会过期。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">9、买了个价格非常昂贵的智能马桶在卫生间里，事后才感觉没什么巨大作用，其实买个一般的也可以了，不用这么浪费钱。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKDfOu8qyUqzUKjw1bscCNZUId8EwyjybP0jOk1Y1X9ic1vzXZbq94j4w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"500\" _width=\"auto\" src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKDfOu8qyUqzUKjw1bscCNZUId8EwyjybP0jOk1Y1X9ic1vzXZbq94j4w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这9条经验是装修的时候最容易犯错误的地方，但很多装修业主通过经历痛苦的教训后才明白，但这个时候已经晚了。如果你准备装修或想装修，可要提前记住哦！</p><p><br/></p>', '家装指南', '1');
