INSERT INTO `tbl_news` VALUES ('32', '20180111\\f23ed45d62c70cc55edac3650d2738496624.png', '卫生间没有窗户，该怎么办？', '管理员', '2018-01-11 13:43:09', '57', '卫生间是每天都会接触到大量水气的空间，都市里，因为生活空间狭小，很多人家里的浴室是没有对外窗的，尤其在套房、小平数，这种情形更常见！\r\n\r\n偏偏夏季闷、湿、热，浴室没有对外窗，可想而知采光通风不良，阴暗、潮湿、发霉等，一堆问题就会接踵而来，所以网络上随便查询，都看得到有人在发问：卫生间无窗该怎么办？   ', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">卫生间是每天都会接触到大量水气的空间，都市里，因为生活空间狭小，很多人家里的浴室是没有对外窗的，尤其在套房、小平数，这种情形更常见！</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">偏偏夏季闷、湿、热，浴室没有对外窗，可想而知采光通风不良，阴暗、潮湿、发霉等，一堆问题就会接踵而来，所以网络上随便查询，都看得到有人在发问：卫生间无窗该怎么办？ &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKr5aRn04mUWZNltYG02WpsUjSFibiaD7JfSTqhDnNvmu1R3icZg0QEmGHw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"500\" _width=\"auto\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKr5aRn04mUWZNltYG02WpsUjSFibiaD7JfSTqhDnNvmu1R3icZg0QEmGHw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果你的卫生间没有对外窗是既定事实，可是偏偏你又不想大动土改变卫生间的方位格局，那以下提供六个简单的解决方案，试着规划你的卫生间，可以让卫生间空间舒爽一点！ &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">一、抽风机 + 暖风机&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">卫生间没有对外窗，最大的问题就是通风不良！没有窗户的前提下，你的卫生间已经失去了自然通风的条件，但总可以用人工方式补足吧！</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">加装可以增加空气流动的抽风机，带走卫浴里的湿气，再补强暖风机，洗完澡开个半小时至一小时，让卫生间可以干得比较快。&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.274\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKRGKqDP6cSiahbEkBg5VGibXSjy6B9vCbRicYiahWibyiaPdwUhCS5e7dibwKw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"500\" _width=\"auto\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKRGKqDP6cSiahbEkBg5VGibXSjy6B9vCbRicYiahWibyiaPdwUhCS5e7dibwKw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">二、浅色系or亮色系&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">卫生间没有对外窗，第二个会遇到的问题是采光不够，没有窗户就是没有采光，此时如果再把卫生间规划为深色系，看起来就会很更阴暗，而浅色系、亮色系可以提亮空间感是大家都知道的，所以没有对外窗的卫生间，乖乖规划成浅色系！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.278\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKG4ibNES5ICCG5cOWicVSuHuyJJNCdeKQvxvOM1dGhyibQvXH5HdYZ8eoA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"500\" _width=\"auto\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKG4ibNES5ICCG5cOWicVSuHuyJJNCdeKQvxvOM1dGhyibQvXH5HdYZ8eoA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">三、镜面&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">通常没有对外窗的卫生间，空间都偏小，镜面有反射的作用，不只可以反射空间，让空间看起来更大，更可以反射光线，补足原本就偏弱的光源，所以适时规划一些镜面是好的，但也不要整间卫生间挂满镜面，反而容易被吓到阿！&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">四、干湿分离or浴帘&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这点，绝对是没有对外窗的卫生间，一定要做到的事！想想，没有对外窗，湿气已经够重了，还把水气湿气搞得整间都是，根本就干不了阿！</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果一开始就没有规划干湿分离了，浴帘也是个补救的好方法，起码还是可以挡掉一些四溅的水花。&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">五、绿色植物&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">有些绿色植物能够吸取湿气，很适合放在卫生间，像是黄金葛，吊兰，猪笼草，都是很常见会摆在卫生间里的植物，摆几盆在浴室里，别说实际功效有多少，光是看着就先令人觉得赏心悦目！&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">六、玻璃取代水泥墙&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">针对这个方案，是要花点功夫的，必须出动工班重整卫生间，所以推荐给有需要装修的人，如果你的卫生间没有对外窗，那对室内的墙面，可以用雾玻璃取代水泥墙，忍容易就可以由室内光源改善卫生间里光线不足的问题！&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.262\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKuLCACSaJWFVQjDMmqAnheoDLr40RdKbgxCHVSMrCh9X01UlPjeCTgg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"500\" _width=\"auto\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/tUk8Unib8hmQ70pTnlRtoyKjEibddAQvjKuLCACSaJWFVQjDMmqAnheoDLr40RdKbgxCHVSMrCh9X01UlPjeCTgg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"><img class=\"__bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.03620689655172414\" data-src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Q49Zv1d8YwYLYvOafOHn5zdF525RqlzJIXsfSiaRRRatswHpv5Ox3iavXXJXUXHTibJ8Ndhw7EGFBeXxiaXyHXQHiaQ/0?wx_fmt=gif\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"580\" title=\"水桶浇花动态分割线\" _width=\"auto\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Q49Zv1d8YwYLYvOafOHn5zdF525RqlzJIXsfSiaRRRatswHpv5Ox3iavXXJXUXHTibJ8Ndhw7EGFBeXxiaXyHXQHiaQ/0?wx_fmt=gif&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" data-order=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"/></span></p><p><br/></p>', '家装指南', '1');
INSERT INTO `tbl_news` VALUES ('33', '20180111\\1a396de5a7f78b981d3957c6d135625944297.png', '软装这么弄，家里不美都不行！', '管理员', '2018-01-11 13:51:02', '56', '软装风为什么日益升温，因为它不用在空间里大兴土木也能得到改头换面的效果，即使主人是非专业人士，只要你对美和生活有热爱，拿出时间学习一些小技巧，可以迅速让你的家摆脱大众脸，变身为有个性有故事有颜值的新空间。', '<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">软装风为什么日益升温，因为它不用在空间里大兴土木也能得到改头换面的效果，即使主人是非专业人士，只要你对美和生活有热爱，拿出时间学习一些小技巧，可以迅速让你的家摆脱大众脸，变身为有个性有故事有颜值的新空间。</p><p><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 8px 12px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 501px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); color: rgb(117, 117, 118);\">点亮空间重点</section></section></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">做整体空间搭配对非专业的主人会有些难度，从点入手会更容易一些，选出要改造空间的重点，可以是一面墙、一处角落、一个阳台、一组灯光或者一个大件家具，然后集中想法进行再设计。</p><p><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;